{"tid":1761313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府撥逾960萬賑濟印度水災災民","createTime":"2019-11-28T23:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T00:25:32.000Z","uid":196719,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b54e88bc394de43870792d5849b6f56ca8e35e","tid":1761313,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T23:38:34.000Z","msg":"政府接納賑災基金諮詢委員會的建議，從賑災基金批出兩項共960萬7千元的撥款，予兩間機構賑濟印度比哈爾邦水災災民。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，印度比哈爾邦水災的受災人數超過2百萬人。兩項撥款分別為510萬8千元予香港仁人家園及449萬9千元予國際培幼會（香港）。撥款會用於提供臨時居所包、食水包和廚具包，以及家庭和衞生用品，約5萬8千多名災民受惠。兩間救援機構將會進行賑災的地點並不相同，並沒有資源重疊。委員會希望撥款為災民提供適切援助，幫助他們早日回復正常生活。<br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495004-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495004-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=0f2066ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495004-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=626664a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495004-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a> <br />\n<br />\n寧願捐印度都唔益香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8798f99873268db8fdb8513bc007b3203f8f705c","tid":1761313,"uid":248044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T23:41:43.000Z","msg":"果班警甴ot錢加埋都多過呢幾球啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a749a17a7a447f01d1a3cf235a9699ba6874c91","tid":1761313,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T23:45:44.000Z","msg":"一千萬都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩人地都會覺得OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a1851d15273ffd025b78feafda29b8d3f0c09f","tid":1761313,"u